title: RHOBH Season 9 Trailer Breakdown
description:
"The Real Housewives of Beverly Hills" is back for a ninth season, and we're here to dissect every shot, frame, and seatbelt in the new trailer. Come join us as we try to figure out just what's going on with these ladies. So much dramz!

See acast.com/privacy for privacy and opt-out information.
